{
  "stem": "21919.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when the baby started crying, they said to her that you have to make that baby stop crying because we're all gonna perish if they hear the baby cry.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So she had to put a pillow in her baby's face and-- and kill her own baby for the others to survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So she was emotional, very emotional about everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said to me, I think I can make arrangements for all those men who are here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you cook for them, wash their clothes for them, you can eat, and you'll have something to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she made arrangements with them that I'll be eating with them for-- for the-- for doing those chores for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those two boys who brought me there said that if I want to go back to school, they can take me with them, and I can stay with them and go to school.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it sounded very good to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she came up and she says, look, you are being very foolish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because one girl with two boys to live in the same house is not a very good thing to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think you're better off to stay with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is where I met my husband, because he was one of the men that stayed in that house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after maybe--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I stayed-- I stayed there for a while, and I got a bit nervous because I used to go to confession, to-- I would go with them to church, and she would say to me, you haven't been to confession.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to go to confession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- I was terrified, because I didn't really know what I'm supposed to confess to, or how I'm supposed to confess to.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
